spell_list.description: Following the natural expiration (triggers or duration) of Vital Intercession, the target will gain increased healing received for a short duration. Repent will also ward for more on that target.
spell_list.description_pvp: Following the natural expiration (triggers or duration) of Vital Intercession, the target will gain increased healing received for a short duration. Repent will also ward for more on that target.

effect_list.description: Vital Intercession will apply an effect that increases healing received by 30% when it expires naturally. If Repent is cast on a target who has Divinity's Aid active, it will also ward 30% more.

spell_list.name: Divinity's Aid
